   To build everything:

      make clean
      make
     
   Library produced:

      libome.a     - various analysis & measurement routines

   Programs produced:

      ome_info     - prints information about an image file.
      ome_make     - creates TIFF test image files.
      ome_copy     - copies image files, possibly altering them.
      ome_hist     - makes graylevel histograms.
      ome_obj      - finds foreground objects.
  
      ome_tmcp     - Calculates avg. distance from dot in an object's center
                     to dots in associated object 'arms'.
      ome_cccp     - Another such measure
    
